equation: assert(1.0 + R1.alpha * (R1.T - R1.T_ref) >= 1e-15, "Temperature outside scope of model!");
assert(1.0 + R2.alpha * (R2.T - R2.T_ref) >= 1e-15, "Temperature outside scope of model!");
assert(1.0 + resistor.alpha * (resistor.T - resistor.T_ref) >= 1e-15, "Temperature outside scope of model!");
assert(1.0 + resistor1.alpha * (resistor1.T - resistor1.T_ref) >= 1e-15, "Temperature outside scope of model!");
assert(1.0 + resistor2.alpha * (resistor2.T - resistor2.T_ref) >= 1e-15, "Temperature outside scope of model!");
assert(1.0 + resistor3.alpha * (resistor3.T - resistor3.T_ref) >= 1e-15, "Temperature outside scope of model!");
0.5 * constantVoltage.V + opAmp1.absSlope * opAmp1.vin / (1.0 + opAmp1.absSlope * smooth(0, if opAmp1.f * opAmp1.vin < 0.0 then (-opAmp1.f) * opAmp1.vin else opAmp1.f * opAmp1.vin))
0.5 * constantVoltage.V + opAmp.absSlope * opAmp.vin / (1.0 + opAmp.absSlope * smooth(0, if opAmp.f * opAmp.vin < 0.0 then (-opAmp.f) * opAmp.vin else opAmp.f * opAmp.vin))
assert(1.0 + R1.alpha * (R1.T - R1.T_ref) >= 1e-15, "Temperature outside scope of model!");
assert(1.0 + R2.alpha * (R2.T - R2.T_ref) >= 1e-15, "Temperature outside scope of model!");
assert(1.0 + resistor.alpha * (resistor.T - resistor.T_ref) >= 1e-15, "Temperature outside scope of model!");
assert(1.0 + resistor1.alpha * (resistor1.T - resistor1.T_ref) >= 1e-15, "Temperature outside scope of model!");
assert(1.0 + resistor2.alpha * (resistor2.T - resistor2.T_ref) >= 1e-15, "Temperature outside scope of model!");
assert(1.0 + resistor3.alpha * (resistor3.T - resistor3.T_ref) >= 1e-15, "Temperature outside scope of model!");
assert(R1.T_ref >= 0.0, "Variable violating min constraint: 0.0 <= R1.T_ref, has value: " + String(R1.T_ref, "g"));
assert(R1.T >= 0.0, "Variable violating min constraint: 0.0 <= R1.T, has value: " + String(R1.T, "g"));
